1
00:00:08,380 --> 00:00:10,090
What's been on your mind?

2
00:00:10,090 --> 00:00:13,680
This handkerchief... is it tacky?

3
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:16,220
Not at all. I love it.

4
00:00:16,220 --> 00:00:18,520
I see.

5
00:00:18,520 --> 00:00:20,520
Wait, are you mad?

6
00:00:20,520 --> 00:00:21,940
No.

7
00:00:21,940 --> 00:00:26,070
Oh yeah, you said you wanted to introduce
me to someone.

8
00:00:26,070 --> 00:00:28,530
Oh, you mean Natsu?

9
00:00:28,530 --> 00:00:29,860
Yeah.

10
00:00:33,530 --> 00:00:37,120
I'm making hot pot at my place later. Want to come?

11
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:40,500
Okay.

12
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:43,000
Coming in.

13
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:47,090
(Yuki and Natsu laughing)

14
00:00:47,090 --> 00:00:49,090
So, how big should these be?

15
00:00:49,090 --> 00:00:50,800
About that size?

16
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:52,050
Oh!

17
00:00:54,050 --> 00:00:56,680
Hi, I'm Kato Natsu.

18
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:59,020
I... I'm Motomiya Makoto.

19
00:00:59,020 --> 00:01:03,230
(Oh no, she has major girlfriend vibes.)

20
00:01:03,230 --> 00:01:07,030
We're in the same grade, right?
So we don't have to be so formal...

21
00:01:07,030 --> 00:01:09,240
Yeah, of course.

22
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:11,450
Great.

23
00:01:12,910 --> 00:01:14,820
Makoto, why were you being so formal all of a sudden?

24
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:17,080
Don't tell me you're nervous.

25
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:20,210
- You're so annoying! I'm going to chop the vegetables.
- See? You're totally nervous.

26
00:01:20,210 --> 00:01:24,000
Hey, you could at least unbutton your shirt.

27
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:30,610
Wow, I never pictured Yuki-kun being so chummy with someone.

28
00:01:30,610 --> 00:01:32,220
You two must be really close.

29
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,840
Oh, be quiet!

30
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:37,850
Hey! How about you two
start with a toast?
